"    • Mountains of Dorth\n"
"    • Mountains of Haag\n"
"    • Greenwood\n"
"    • Silent Forest\n"
"    • Forest of Thelien\n"
"    • River Oumph\n"
"    • River Bork\n"
"    • Frosty Wastes\n"
